N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 8 ยง 75.6 - Examination in audiology

State Regulations

The department may accept grades satisfactory to the State

Board for Speech-Language Pathology and Audiology on an examination determined
by the department to be acceptable for licensure as an
audiologist. Notes
